Who do you think you are!

21
00:01:27,787 --> 00:01:28,955
Get out!

22
00:01:28,955 --> 00:01:30,081
Yes!

23
00:01:32,859 --> 00:01:36,818
I can't do anything.
Teacher Popson was right.

24
00:01:44,170 --> 00:01:46,639
The first aid for bullet wounds.

25
00:01:46,639 --> 00:01:48,675
War is coming.

26
00:01:48,675 --> 00:01:50,802
Is that why
we need to attend this calss?

27
00:01:55,815 --> 00:01:58,651
