32
00:02:10,563 --> 00:02:12,665
This is chance for them to learn

33
00:02:12,665 --> 00:02:15,862
Give me two good trainees

34
00:02:16,503 --> 00:02:17,629
Please...

35
00:02:17,871 --> 00:02:20,173
Blanny and Natalie

36
00:02:20,173 --> 00:02:22,108
Assist Doctor Popson
with his operation

37
00:02:22,108 --> 00:02:23,042
Yes!

38
00:02:23,042 --> 00:02:25,533
The rest do some self-study.

39
00:02:26,513 --> 00:02:30,083
What are you doing?
Go get some self-study.

40
00:02:30,083 --> 00:02:31,414
Yes!

41
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:41,659
Candy!

42
00:02:45,899 --> 00:02:48,629
No, It's Impossible!

43
00:02:52,672 --> 00:02:54,874
