were late for class.

69
00:04:40,580 --> 00:04:41,848
That is because...

70
00:04:41,848 --> 00:04:43,249
Natalie is not any better.

71
00:04:43,249 --> 00:04:45,585
She faints when she sees blood.

72
00:04:45,585 --> 00:04:46,986
